    "TraditionalChinese": "高能量物質"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "A stable, crystalline form of hydrogen remarkable both for its extreme energy density and its stability at atmospheric pressures.<br><br>Common to all worlds, Di-hydrogen is found in the form of large <span class=\"name name-technology\">blue crystals</span>. It is a key component of <span class=\"name name-commodity\">Starship Launch Fuel</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "氢的一种稳定晶体形式，特点是能量密度极大，而且在大气压力下也能保持稳定。<br><br>二氢在所有星球都很常见，通常以大块的<span class=\"name name-technology\">蓝色晶体</span>形式存在。它是<span class=\"name name-commodity\">飞船发射燃料</span>的关键成分。",
    "TencentChinese": "氢的一种稳定晶体形式，特点是能量密度极大，而且在大气压力下也能保持稳定。<br><br>二氢在所有星球都很常见，通常以大块的<span class=\"name name-technology\">蓝色晶体</span>形式存在。它是<span class=\"name name-commodity\">飞船发射燃料</span>的关键成分。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "穩定、晶狀體的氫，具有極高能量密度，且在大氣壓力下保持穩定。<br><br>二氫在所有星球上都很常見，普遍會以大型<span class=\"name name-technology\">藍色晶體</span>形式出現。是<span class=\"name name-commodity\">太空船驅動燃料</span>的重要元素之一。"
  },
